    <div class="col-md-12">
        <p> The nearby bookstore also caught our attention - a new book also made its way into our bag. Then we returned to the restaurant from the morning. The decision to eat there turned out to be spot on - the food was excellent, the ambiance was perfect, and we stayed for quite a while. </p>
        <p> In the afternoon, we continued to Lübbenau. A short detour initially led us to a repo market, but without any great finds. Our planned parking spot for the night was directly opposite - in front of a hotel with a swimming pool. </p>
        <p> Since we had no desire for the motorhome that day, we decided to visit the hotel bar without further ado. With a drink, a pleasant atmosphere and the new book, we let the day fade away. </p>
        <p> Back in the camper, we prepared a late dinner, watched a film and ended the day relaxed. </p>
